{"tid":2250361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有颱風來襲啦","createTime":"2020-10-20T05:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T05:12:07.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"98411e60f4065b5668396f5b4814705908d75296","tid":2250361,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:09:19.000Z","msg":"颱風「浪卡」上周襲港，猶幸未有明顯破壞。天文台今早表示，一個位於菲律賓以東海域的熱帶低氣壓已增強為熱帶風暴，並命名為沙德爾。在今早10時，沙德爾集結在馬尼拉之東北偏東約370公里，預料向西移動，時速約28公里，之後會進入南海中部，向越南中部及海南島推進。<br />\n<br />\n天文台熱帶氣旋路徑圖顯示，預測沙德爾會今明兩日掠過呂宋島，在周四(22日)進入本港800公里範圍，有機會在<span class=\"red\">周六(24日)</span>升格為颱風，同時最接近本港。<br />\n「沙德爾」是太平洋島國米克羅尼西亞提供的名字，是當地波納佩島傳說將領蘇迪羅之可靠守衛或士兵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2781397/%E3%80%90%E9%A2%A8%E5%86%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%99%82%E3%80%91%E7%86%B1%E5%B8%B6%E6%B0%A3%E6%97%8B%E6%B2%99%E5%BE%B7%E7%88%BE%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%8E%E6%A9%AB%E9%81%8E%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%20%E6%B8%AF%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%88%96%E5%86%8D%E6%89%93%E9%A2%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2781397%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%2599%2582%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2586%25B1%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%2597%258B%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%2588%25BE%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%25BE%258B%25E8%25B3%2593%2520%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25A2%25A8&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=0daa5026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2781397/%E3%80%90%E9%A2%A8%E5%86%8D%E8%B5%B7%E6%99%82%E3%80%91%E7%86%B1%E5%B8%B6%E6%B0%A3%E6%97%8B%E6%B2%99%E5%BE%B7%E7%88%BE%E4%BB%8A%E6%98%8E%E6%A9%AB%E9%81%8E%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%20%E6%B8%AF%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E6%88%96%E5%86%8D%E6%89%93%E9%A2%A8</a>"},{"pid":"7a9a6abc73ba50b1419ce04b75c66feaaec88988","tid":2250361,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco